The new site will feature enhanced navigation, improved search capabilities, 
and other improvements designed to make CERA.com a more valuable experience 
for our Clients.

We hope you will take the opportunity to visit the site in the near future. 
After you have reviewed the Website, please take the time to complete a brief 
online survey at: http://beta.cera.com/survey/

Please note that this site has been made available for demonstration purposes 
only. CERA's current research and analysis will continue to be featured on 
http://www.cera.com/? 

Your participation is appreciated! Your input will help us to deliver a new 
and improved Web-based experience for you, our client user community.

